CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 25, 1960, pg. A11 reads: "7. Delicious snacks of sausage tid-bits attracted many to the Metropolitan Sausage C. booth. Representatives were Duke Tucker, Mrs. Viola M. Parker, manager, and Dolores and William Covington."
